---
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
numberOfLatestPostsToShow: 4
---
<h1>Mark Dyck is a baker who writes.</h1>

{% set postsCount = collections.posts | length %}
{% set latestPostsCount = postsCount | min(numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}

<h2>Latest {{ latestPostsCount }} Post{% if latestPostsCount != 1 %}s{% endif %}</h2>


{% set recentposts = collections.posts | head(-1 * numberOfLatestPostsToShow) %}

{% set postslist = recentposts | reverse %}  {# postslists.njk displays posts in the order you provide them#}

{% set postslistCounter = postsCount %}  {# used to number the posts being listed #}

{% include "postslist.njk" %}

{% set morePosts = postsCount - numberOfLatestPostsToShow %}
{% if morePosts > 0 %}
<p>There are {{ morePosts }} more post{% if morePosts != 1 %}s{% endif %} in <a href="/blog/">the journal</a>.</p>
{% endif %}

List every content page in the project 

<ul>
	{%- for entry in collections.all %}
	<li><a href="{{ entry.url }}"><code>{{ entry.url }}</code></a></li>
	{%- endfor %}
</ul>

